    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented minimum evidence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion was satisfied across all evaluated configurations. The UnitOfAssurance is accepted for regulatory submission supporting 510(k) clearance.",
